              "messages": {
                "default": [
                  {
                    "cta": "Next!",
                    "text": "Hey! Today we will learn how to handle objections at work.\nSometimes a client or colleague disagrees with your idea.\nYou need to respond politely and give a new perspective.",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4c60d21b-5871-4a24-b216-c5b37509852f-Objection-Handling---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Got it!",
                    "text": "First, acknowledge their point and then reframe it.\nUse: 'I see your point, but from [angle], [reframed point].'\nExample: 'I see your point, but from a long-term view, this saves money.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4c60d21b-5871-4a24-b216-c5b37509852f-Objection-Handling---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Makes sense!",
                    "text": "Next, explain why you suggested something.\nUse: 'We suggested [option] because [benefit].'\nExample: 'We suggested the yearly plan because it costs 30% less per month.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4c60d21b-5871-4a24-b216-c5b37509852f-Objection-Handling---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Nice!",
                    "text": "You can also share what others have experienced.\nUse: 'Other clients in [field] found that [result].'\nExample: 'Other clients in edtech found that good onboarding reduces drop-offs.'",
                    "media": {
                      "url": "https://r2-activity-data.gosupernova.live/system-uploads/scenario-data/4c60d21b-5871-4a24-b216-c5b37509852f-Objection-Handling---2.jpg",
                      "type": "image"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "cta": "Start Practice!",
                    "text": "Now let's practice handling objections using these structures!",
                    "media": {
